author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Evolution Gaming launches Live Casino for Casumo
text:
Oct 8 Evolution Gaming Group publ AB :
* Launches Live Casino for Casumo
* Has signed deal to offer full line-up of Live Casino games for Casumo.com
* Casumo is one of biggest and fastest growing operators in Northern Europe and also recently entered regulated UK market
